credit policy by permitting a modest decline in the interest rate on
federal funds, overnight loans between banks.
   Windmere dropped 2~ to 13\. The company said its manufacturing
and shipping activities in the Far East have been curtailed by the
effects of the political turmoil in China.
   The NYSE's composite index of all its listed common stocks gained
1.13 to 182.06. At the American Stock Exchange, the market value
index was up 2.90 at 363.74.
   Volume on the Big Board came to 151.08 million shares with two
hours to go.
