   Stock prices gained ground for the second
straight session Wednesday in a busy session energized by two
takeover bids in the communications industry.
   The Dow Jones average of 30 industrials climbed 16.00 to 2,512.32
on top of Tuesday's 15.62-point rise.
   Advancing issues outnumbered declines by about 9 to 5 in
nationwide trading of New York Stock Exchange-listed stocks, with
